AUSTRALIA: RTRS-Costello says Australia growth uneven.RTRS-Costello says Australia growth uneven.Australian Treasurer Peter Costello said on Wednesday that growth was probably uneven across the national economy.  "I think there's probably uneven growth in the economy," Costello said in a radio interview."The service sector is doing better, the mining sector is doing better and there's been a recovery in the rural sector."But, he added, the budget aimed to help the small business sector by giving tax relief.The Reserve Bank of Australia's 50 basis-point cut in the official cash rate on July 31 would also boost confidence and assist small business, he said.-- Canberra Newsroom 616-273-2730